The following was already implemented:
- **Prometheus Registry** (`internal/shared/telemetry/prometheus/registry.go`)
- **HTTP Metrics** (`internal/shared/telemetry/prometheus/metrics.go`)
- **Database Metrics** (`internal/shared/telemetry/prometheus/db.go`)
- **Redis Metrics** (`internal/shared/telemetry/prometheus/redis.go`)
