### 5. Database Migrations
Observability tables already exist (`migrations/001_create_observability_tables.up.sql`):
- `observability_metrics` - Historical metric data
- `alert_history` - Alert tracking
- `quota_usage` - Quota tracking
- `audit_log_enrichment` - Trace context for audit logs
- `service_performance_daily` - Daily performance aggregates
- `sla_compliance` - SLA tracking

